contentrichtext.text: {{Infobox road |province=QC |type=QC |route=233 |maint=[[Transports Québec]] |map=Route 233-QC.png |established= |decommissioned= |alternate_name= |length_km=34.2 |length_round= 1 |length_ref=<ref>Ministère des transports, "Distances routières", page 86, Les Publications du Québec, 2005</ref> |direction_b=North |direction_a=South |terminus_b={{jct|state=QC|QC|231}} in [[Saint-Damase, Montérégie, Quebec|Saint-Damase]] |terminus_a={{jct|state=QC|QC|104}} in [[Farnham, Quebec|Farnham]] |previous_type=QC |previous_route=232 |next_type=QC |next_route=234 |junction= {{jct|state=QC|QC|112}} in Saint-Césaire <br> {{jct|state=QC|A|10}} in Sainte-Brigide d'Iberville |}} '''Route 233''' is a [[provincial highway]] located in the [[Montérégie]] region of [[Quebec]] east of [[Montreal]]. The highway links Farnham and Saint-Césaire with Saint-Hyacinther. It starts at a junction with [[Quebec Route 104|Route 104]] between Farnham and Sainte-Brigide-d'Iberville, next to a training facility of the [[Canadian Forces]] and runs north toward a [[parclo]] interchange with [[Quebec Autoroute 10|Autoroute 10]] after which it crosses the [[Rivière du Sud-Ouest]] which it follows for a few kilometers until its headwaters on [[Yamaska River]]. Shortly after it runs through Saint-Césaire, crossing [[Quebec Route 112|Route 112]], before continuing to follow the Yamaska until its end at the junction of [[Quebec Route 231|Route 231]]. ==Municipalities along Route 233== * [[Farnham, Quebec|Farnham]] * [[Sainte-Brigide-d'Iberville, Quebec|Sainte-Brigide-d'Iberville]] * [[Saint-Césaire, Quebec|Saint-Césaire]] * [[Saint-Damase, Montérégie, Quebec|Saint-Damase]] ==See also== * [[List of Quebec provincial highways]] ==References== {{reflist}} == External links == * [http://www.inforoutiere.qc.ca/fr/carte_routiere/index.asp Official Transports Quebec Provincial Road Network Map] {{fr icon}} * [http://maps.google.com/maps?f=d&hl=en&geocode=9993328783196024978,45.289868,-73.014202%3B2192994359694954459,45.561220,-72.980510&saddr=RTE-233+%4045.289868,+-73.014202&daddr=45.377714,-73.036423+to:Rang+du+Bas-De-La-Rivi%C3%A8re%2FRTE-233+%4045.561220,+-72.980510&mra=dpe&mrcr=0&mrsp=1&sz=11&via=1&doflg=ptk&sll=45.38109,-72.91008&sspn=0.217031,0.601501&ie=UTF8&ll=45.444717,-72.954712&spn=0.433574,1.203003&z=10Route 233] on GoogleMaps <br> {{Secondary Highways in Quebec (200-series)}} [[Category:Quebec Routes|233]] {{Quebec-road-stub}}
